
---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Justice Thinker" description="Learn about Justice Thinker's journey as a physicist, developer, and polymath">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        About Justice Thinker
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A polymath dedicated to pushing the boundaries of knowledge across physics, technology, and human communication.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none reveal">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-700 rounded-xl p-8 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Journey of a Polymath</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          My path has been defined by an insatiable curiosity and a refusal to be confined by traditional boundaries. 
          As a physicist, I explore the fundamental laws that govern our universe. As a developer, I build technologies 
          that solve real-world problems. As a thinker and speaker, I engage in the art of persuasion and the 
          pursuit of truth through debate and discourse.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg reveal">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">üî¨ Physics & Research</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            My work in physics focuses on bridging theoretical frameworks with practical applications. 
            From experimental setups to computational models, I'm passionate about understanding 
            the deeper mechanics of reality and translating complex concepts into actionable insights.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg reveal">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">üíª Technology & Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            In the realm of technology, I specialize in AI and machine learning applications, 
            web development, and creating systems that enhance human capabilities. My projects 
            like Look-Out and Overmind represent my commitment to building intelligent solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Core Philosophy</h2>
        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6 italic text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          "True innovation happens at the intersection of disciplines. By refusing to be confined 
          to a single field, we open ourselves to solutions that others might never see."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          My approach to problem-solving is fundamentally interdisciplinary. I believe that the most 
          breakthrough innovations emerge when we apply insights from physics to programming challenges, 
          or when we use debate techniques to structure scientific arguments. This polymath perspective 
          has been the driving force behind my most successful projects and research endeavors.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-blue-800/20 rounded-xl reveal">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üèÜ</div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Speaking & Debate</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Championship debater, coach, and judge with a passion for the art of persuasion and critical thinking.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 dark:from-purple-900/20 dark:to-purple-800/20 rounded-xl reveal">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üß™</div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Research & Innovation</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Conducting cutting-edge research that bridges theoretical physics with practical applications.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 dark:from-green-900/20 dark:to-green-800/20 rounded-xl reveal">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üöÄ</div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Technology Leadership</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Building AI-powered solutions and leading technological innovations that solve real-world problems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-8 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">What Drives Me</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mt-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <strong>Curiosity:</strong> An unending desire to understand how things work, from quantum mechanics 
              to human psychology, and everything in between.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mt-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <strong>Impact:</strong> Building technologies and sharing knowledge that make a meaningful 
              difference in people's lives and advance human understanding.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <strong>Growth:</strong> Constantly learning, adapting, and pushing beyond comfort zones 
              to explore new frontiers of knowledge and capability.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>